1. Open the transactions page (http://localhost:3000/user-portal/2)
2. Make note of all existing transactions
3. Refresh the browser 
4. Verify all transactions persisted
5. Close the browser comletely
6. Re-open the browser and login (if forced)
7. Verify all transactions persisted
8. Stop the backend from running
9. Restart the backend
10. Login
11. Verify the transactions persisted
